VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'consistent. Again, we get up to that 5-second thing, and that\'s where things start breaking down a bit. But again, I do want to point out that, you know, on that initial rotation, it actually does do a pretty good job there. It really isn\'t until after he steps out of the'

[11:04] [scene:talk]
